restructureit.qualitymeasurement

Class QualityReport

  • java.lang.Object
    • restructureit.qualitymeasurement.QualityReport

  • public class QualityReport
extends java.lang.Object
    Quality report contains the results of refactoring a project. Metrics before and after are stored as well as details of changes in individual quality metrics and what refactorings were applied and how many times they were applied.
    Author:
    Pamela
